<Body> 
	<Title>安徽宿州“跨省污染”事件处理:废料及土壤作无害化处理 公安机关刑事立案</Title>  
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2013年06月04日15:59:47</ReportTime>  
	<Content> 
		<Paragraph> 
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"> 
					<Participant sid="s1">新华网</Participant>  
					<Location lid="l1">合肥</Location>  
					<Time tid="t1" type="relTime">６月４日</Time>  
					<Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter>（记者程士华）
				</Event> 
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent"> 
					<Participant sid="s2">记者</Participant>  
					<Time tid="t2" type="relTime">４日</Time>从 
					<Location lid="l2">安徽省宿州市埇桥区</Location>  
					<Participant oid="o2">政府</Participant>  
					<Denoter did="d2" type="statement">获悉</Denoter> 
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e3"> 
					<Time tid="t3" type="relTime">近日</Time>发生 
					<Location lid="l3">在埇桥区</Location>的 
					<Object oid="o3">跨省倾倒危险废料污染事件现场</Object>  
					<Denoter did="d3" type="action">处置工作已经基本清理结束</Denoter> 
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e4"> 
					<Object oid="o4">近百吨危险废料及数百吨被污染土壤</Object>被委托给 
					<Participant sid="s4">专业公司</Participant>  
					<Denoter did="d4" type="operation">进行无害化处理</Denoter> 
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e5"> 
					<Participant sid="s5">公安机关</Participant>已经对 
					<Object oid="o5">此刑事</Object>  
					<Denoter did="d5" type="action">立案</Denoter> 
				</Event>。
			</Sentence> 
		</Paragraph>  
		<Paragraph> 
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent"> 
					<Time tid="t6" type="relTime">５月２５日１０时许</Time>， 
					<Participant sid="s6">埇桥区环保局</Participant>  
					<Denoter did="d6" type="action">接到举报，反映</Denoter> 
				</Event>  
				<Event eid="e7"> 
					<Location lid="l7">解集乡解集村</Location>有 
					<Participant sid="s7">人</Participant>将 
					<Object oid="o7">成车的“废油”</Object>  
					<Denoter did="d7" type="action">倾倒</Denoter> 
				</Event>  
				<Event eid="e8"> 
					<Location lid="l8">在大坑里</Location>并 
					<Denoter did="d8" type="action">焚烧</Denoter> 
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e9"> 
					<Participant sid="s9">气味</Participant>  
					<Denoter did="d9" type="perception">难闻</Denoter> 
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e10"> 
					<Participant sid="s10">环保部门</Participant>  
					<Time tid="t10" type="relTime">立即</Time>  
					<Denoter did="d10" type="action">前往控制</Denoter>  
					<Location lid="l10">现场</Location> 
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e11"> 
					<Denoter did="d11" type="action">采样</Denoter> 
				</Event>  
				<Event eid="e12">送 
					<Participant sid="s12">交省环保厅</Participant>  
					<Denoter did="d12" type="action">分析化验</Denoter> 
				</Event>， 
				<Event eid="e13"> 
					<Denoter did="d13">初步确定</Denoter>  
					<Object sid="s13">危险废物</Object>为 
					<Object oid="o13">医药或农药或化妆品生产中间体的残留物</Object>，为苯酚类物质，有臭味，有一定毒性，其中有机毒害品具有可燃性，遇明火、高热或与氧化剂接触会燃烧爆炸，并会释放出有毒气体
				</Event>。
			</Sentence> 
		</Paragraph> 
	</Content>  
